sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as User (Client LBP)
    participant Browser as Browser (App Ma Banque LBP)
    participant Client as Client (Frontend LBP)
    participant AS as Authorization Server LBP
    participant RS as Resource Server LBP

    User->>Browser: 1. Initie un virement loyer 650 EUR vers Dupont Jean

    Note over Client: 2. Prépare authorization_details RAR (RFC 9396)<br/>type: payment_initiation, amount: 650.00 EUR,<br/>creditorName: Dupont Jean, creditorIban: FR7612345600012345678901,<br/>remittanceInfo: Loyer Mars 2024

    Client->>AS: 3. POST /as/par (RFC 9126)<br/>response_type: code, client_id, scope: openid payment:initiate,<br/>code_challenge PKCE S256, authorization_details: [...]

    AS-->>Client: 4. { request_uri: urn:ietf:params:oauth:request_uri:XYZ, expires_in: 60 }

    Client->>Browser: 5. Redirect /authorize?client_id=lbp-app&request_uri=urn:...XYZ

    Browser->>AS: 6. GET /authorize
    AS->>AS: 7. Recupere authorization_details depuis request_uri

    AS->>Browser: 8. Affiche page de consentement avec details RAR
    Note over AS,Browser: CONFIRMATION DE VIREMENT<br/>Beneficiaire : Dupont Jean<br/>IBAN : FR76...8901<br/>Montant : 650,00 EUR<br/>Motif : Loyer Mars 2024<br/>Affichage AVANT SCA obligatoire (Art.5 RTS DSP2)

    User->>AS: 9. Confirme + SCA via empreinte digitale (FIDO2)
    AS->>AS: 10. Dynamic Linking: HMAC(cle_User, 65000 || FR7612345600012345678901 || 20240315)

    AS->>Browser: 11. Redirect lbp-app://callback?code=CODE&state=S&iss=https://as.lbp.fr

    Browser->>Client: 12. Retourne code au Client

    Client->>AS: 13. POST /token { code, code_verifier, DPoP-Proof RFC 9449 }
    AS-->>Client: 14. { access_token DPoP-bound avec authorization_details, token_type: DPoP }

    Client->>RS: 15. POST /payments<br/>Authorization: DPoP access_token<br/>DPoP: new DPoP-Proof<br/>Body: { creditorIban: FR76...8901, amount: 650.00, remittanceInfo: Loyer Mars 2024 }

    RS->>RS: 16. Valide DPoP binding<br/>Verifie authorization_details == body<br/>Idempotency check (Idempotency-Key header)

    RS-->>Client: 17. { paymentId: PAY-2024-LBP-001, status: AcceptedSettlementInProcess }

    Client->>Browser: 18. Affiche confirmation virement

    Browser-->>User: 19. Virement confirme - Loyer Mars 2024 - 650,00 EUR

    Note over Client,RS: Token a usage unique - scope payment:initiate one-shot
    Note over AS,Browser: RGPD : journaliser consentement + timestamp + IP + device
